Family Health System Inc saidThe Federal Bankruptcy Court in Fort Worth, Texas has approvedits offer to purchase &lt;Sheppard Dental Centers Inc's> assetsfrom a Chapter 7 bankruptcy proceeding for about 300,000 dlrs.    FHS administers and markets multiple office dentalpractices in the Dallas metropolitan area as well as dentaloffices in the Dallas Metroplex.    The company said it plans to open 12 locations in Dallas bythe end of 1987. Reuter&#3;